web_snippets: A leading voice of the harp today, harpist, composer and educator Brandee Younger defies genres and labels. Recently signed to Impulse! Records.
Brandee Younger is a harpist, composer and bandleader whose music connects spiritual jazz and classical training to the rhythmic soulfulness of R&B and hip-hop.
